data.description: Adorable 3bed/2ba home that has just had a brand new roof installed on June 15, 2023. Also, the sprinkler system has just been maintained and is fully functional to bring live back to the newly seeded backyard. This house also has an additional 410  square ft. Sunroom off the back of the house for afternoon entertainment. Great location close to hospital, schools, shopping and downtown, etc.
